Follow the steps given in this document in order to run the project

	1. Install simplescalar(if it is not installed in the system)
		- Open a terminal and go to the project folder
		- run ./Install-SimpleScalar.sh (if the Install-SimpleScalar.sh is not executale make it execuatble by chmod +x Install-SimpleScalar.sh)
	
	2. Generate the MIPS assembly code by running configure.sh
		- ./configure.sh
		
	 
